div.div: Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken 2nd Season Part 2
The second cour of Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken 2nd Season.

How can you fall in love when you cant even hold hands? Due to a childhood curse, anything that the Duke touches will diewhich makes his flirty maids behavior all the more shocking! Is there a way for the Duke and his companions to somehow break the curse, or is he doomed to a life where love is forever out of his reach?
(Source: Funimation)

Ooyama-kun normally doesnt get involved with Akutsu-san, a delinquent girl in his class, but for some reason she makes his house her hang-out place! Will Ooyama do something horrible to her behind closed doors or will he chase her out? But dealing with Akutsu-sans sexy, cute behavior in such a confined space hes sure to get flustered! He wants her to go home, but he doesnt? A teasing comedy under a single roof!

As players of Monster Hunter and Dungeons & Dragons know, the slime is not exactly the king of the fantasy monsters. So when a 37-year-old Tokyo salaryman dies and wakes up in a world of dragons and magic, he's a little disappointed to find he's become a blind, boneless slime monster.
(Source: Kodansha USA)
